'''小花大翼橙'''(''Citrus micrantha'')是一种野生的[[柑橘属|柑橘属]]植物，属于[[大翼橙|大翼橙]]类，源自[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]南部，特别是[[宿务省|宿务省]]和[[薄荷省|薄荷省]]的岛屿。 两种[[变种|变种]]已被发现：'''小花大翼橙''' (''C. micrantha'' var. ''micrantha'')，俗称'''''biasong'''''，和 '''小果大翼橙''' (''C. micrantha'' var. ''microcarpa'') ，俗称 '''samuyao'''。<ref name=Wester>{{citation |url=http://www.gutenberg.org/files/35816/35816-h/35816-h.htm#pb21 |title=Citrus Fruits In The Philippines |journal=Philippine Agricultural Review |volume=8 |year=1915 |author=P. J. Wester |accessdate=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161438/http://www.gutenberg.org/files/35816/35816-h/35816-h.htm#pb21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{citation |chapter-url=http://citruspages.free.fr/papedas.html#smallfloweredpapeda |chapter=Small-flowered and Small-fruited papeda |title=Citrus Pages |author=Jorma Koskinen |accessdate=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2015-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031075947/http://citruspages.free.fr/papedas.html#smallfloweredpapeda |dead-url=no }}</ref>

小花大翼橙是[[青柠|青柠]]的{{le|祖种|Progenitor}}。 <ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Khan |first1=Iqrar A. |first2=Jude W.|last2=Grosser|title=Regeneration and characterization of somatic hybrid plants of Citrus sinensis (sweet orange) and Citrus micrantha, a progenitor species of lime. |pages=271–278 |date=2004-05-01 |journal=Euphytica |volume=137 |issue=2|doi=10.1023/B:EUPH.0000041591.65333.3c|publisher=Kluwer Academic Publishers|s2cid=12880471 |issn=1573-5060}}</ref> 小花大翼橙和[[马蜂橙|马蜂橙]]可能是[[异名|异名]]，但后者的基因组数据不足以得出明确的结论。 <ref>{{cite chapter |chapter=''Citrus'' taxonomy |last1=Ollitrault |first1=Patrick |last2=Curk |first2=Franck |last3=Krueger |first3=Robert |title=The Citrus Genus |editor-last1=Talon |editor-first1=Manuel |editor-last2=Caruso |editor-first2=Marco |editor-last3=Gmitter |editor-first3=Fred G, Jr. |publisher=Elsevier |year=2020 |pages=57–81 |isbn=9780128121634 |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2wo4swEACAAJ&pg=PA57 |doi=10.1016/B978-0-12-812163-4.00004-8 |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2021-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210704220034/https://books.google.com/books?id=2wo4swEACAAJ&pg=PA57 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

